exceptions.exn: In environment x, y : R p, q : Z a, b : R H3 : y = snd (a, b) /\\ cond_pqb p q Unable to unify "snd (a, b)" with "y".

original: intros x y. intros H. unfold in_ucp_set in H. unfold in_ucp_set. unfold in_ucp_setb in H. destruct H as [p [q H1]]. destruct H1 as [H2 H3]. exists p, q. split. destruct (ucp p q) as [a b]. destruct H2. left. split. reflexivity. reflexivity. destruct H2. right. split. symmetry. apply H. reflexivity. apply H3. apply H3.
